Package ure.terrain

Class TerrainI

  • java.lang.Object
    • ure.terrain.TerrainI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, UTerrain, UAnimator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Blank, Door, Lava, Pit, Stairs, Water
    public abstract class TerrainI
extends java.lang.Object
implements UTerrain, java.lang.Cloneable, UAnimator
    Created by gilmore on 6/20/2018. A real serializable instance of a terrain which exists in a single cell. For API reference when extending this class to create custom terrain types, see the method docs of TerrainDeco.
